#

Warm Roasted Vegetable Salad with Lemon-Tahini Dressing

$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

Sesame

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Tags:

SaladRoasted VegetablesHealthy

Description

A vibrant medley of roasted seasonal vegetables drizzled with a zesty lemon-tahini dressing for a nutritious and satisfying salad.

Ingredients

  • Zucchini: 1 medium
  • Red Bell Pepper: 1
  • Carrot: 1 large
  • Red Onion: 1/2
  • Cherry Tomatoes: 1 cup
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Tahini: 3 tablespoons
  • Lemon Juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 1 clove
  • Water: to thin
  • Fresh Parsley: for garnish
